    "description": "<strong>欢迎来到《Jurassic Park: Survival》！</strong><br><br>在1993年经典巨制《侏罗纪公园》剧情结束的第二天，重返努布拉岛，踏上纵贯6500万年的原创冒险之旅。<br><br>在这款单人动作冒险游戏中，扮演未能从努布拉岛撤离的InGen集团科学家玛雅·乔希博士，揭示一段从未讲述过的故事。<br><br>在和各种恐龙惊心动魄的遭遇中，体验这些史前巨兽的神奇与危险。这些恐龙根据约翰·哈蒙德博士的构想创造而成，每一种都以其独特的行为方式适应这个世界。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索努布拉岛</h2>在完整重现的努布拉岛上开启冒险，这里充满了会做出真实反应的野生动物、恐龙和其他意想不到的危险。从高高矗立的标志性大门，到游客中心和其他建筑物，整座侏罗纪公园将在本作中得到前所未有的真实呈现。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/4b98de854b5bffe3b614a02015b0972d.poster.avif?t=1755181567\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/4b98de854b5bffe3b614a02015b0972d.webm?t=1755181567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/4b98de854b5bffe3b614a02015b0972d.mp4?t=1755181567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >躲避史前猎食者</h2>与电影中的经典恐龙斗智斗勇，逃离它们的追猎。在这场冒险中，你要运用聪明才智，借助引开恐龙和潜行等方式，在一次次紧张刺激、令人难忘的遭遇中躲开这些致命巨兽的血盆大口。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/1ace0e9997192844b3e9a0554fb88e7c.poster.avif?t=1755181567\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/1ace0e9997192844b3e9a0554fb88e7c.webm?t=1755181567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/1ace0e9997192844b3e9a0554fb88e7c.mp4?t=1755181567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在努布拉岛上生存</h2>探索公园，面对危险。运用你能支配的一切资源找到聪明的解决方案，这样才能经受住努布拉岛上无处不在的威胁的考验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/9db50734868c289a7a7ba882efaa5dd0.poster.avif?t=1755181567\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/9db50734868c289a7a7ba882efaa5dd0.webm?t=1755181567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208810/extras/9db50734868c289a7a7ba882efaa5dd0.mp4?t=1755181567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
